<br>
Fortitude? Less HP and AC than HB but lasts for 2hr 45min for more mana?<br>
<br>
Does this make sense?<br>
<br>
Or another couple spells ... Remove Curse and Greater Remove Curse. Are these even worth the trouble? I have no clue. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=584766" target="top"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.members.shaw.ca/Eryenne/Eryennesig.jpg" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
